SubjectBy-election - Outremont, Burnaby South and York–Simcoe
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of OUTREMONT, Quebec, BURNABY SOUTH, British Columbia, and YORK–SIMCOE, Ontario, with polling to take place on February 25, 2019.
